<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Refund Notification</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 20px;">

    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #fff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
        <h2 style="color: #333;">Refund Notification</h2>
        <p>Dear [Customer Name],</p>
        <p>We would like to inform you that a refund has been initiated for your recent purchase.</p>
        <p>Transaction Details:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Order ID:</strong> [Order ID]</li>
            <li><strong>Amount:</strong> [Refund Amount]</li>
            <li><strong>Refund Reason:</strong> [Reason for Refund]</li>
        </ul>
        <p>The refunded amount will be credited back to your original payment method within [Number of Days] business days.</p>
        <p>If you have any questions or concerns regarding this refund, please don't hesitate to contact our customer support team at [Customer Support Email].</p>
        <p>Thank you for your understanding.</p>
        <p>Sincerely,</p>
        <p>[Your Company Name]</p>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
